Package: handyGPlots
Title: Useful functions for generating nice genetics plots in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jack", "Murzynowski", , "jram4@cam.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A series of useful tools and plotting functions for fetching gene structure from Ensembl and UniProt,
    and plotting lolliplots of variant or domain-level association results overlaid on gene/transcript structure.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
